  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 394e3525f288a3649be30b055ab1ef28, type: 3}
  m_Name: Admiration
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: Assembly-CSharp::DialogueNode
  npcName: FresnoNightCrawler
  _lines:
  - You're not afraid to speak your mind...
  - I like that.
  - Keeps me on my toes.
  - Well, back in the day, Fresno used to be legit...
  - But the system only keeps pushing against the little guy...
  - People like you and me...
  - It's why we need to stand up and say something, no matter the cost!
  - Wouldn't you agree?
  _playerReplyOptions:
  - They'll hear me loud and clear!
  - I'll watch from the sidelines...
